headline.main: Eastern Libya Forces Strike From Air, Aim to Retake Oil Site
headline.print_headline: Eastern Libya Forces Strike From Air, Aim to Retake Oil Site

lead_paragraph: Libyan armed forces based in the east launched more airstrikes Saturday against militias that seized oil terminals a day earlier, a spokesman said, accusing troops from the country's rival west of launching a war.
